doc.after: In March 1996 the presidents of Kenya Tanzania and Uganda re established the East African Community EAC The EAC s objectives include harmonising tariffs and customs regimes free movement of people and improving regional infrastructures In March 2004 the three East African countries signed a Customs Union Agreement
